snippet.title: Retale | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2995190/Retale/

This was a 3+ year project that I'm so excited to announce is so close to release!! Visuals by @GarrettTheCarrot, development and code by @thirteenling and music composed by my brother gavin and @kylecarvelle ! This is our very first game, so don't expect perfection, but for a first game I'd say we did pretty darn good😎 however make sure to send any feedback to gtcarrot.create@gmail.com!
